.SH NAME
Specio::DeclaredAt \- A class to represent where a type or coercion was declared
.SH VERSION
.IX Header "VERSION"
version 0.48
.SH SYNOPSIS
.IX Header "SYNOPSIS"
.Vb 1
\&    my $declared = Specio::DeclaredAt\->new_from_caller(1);
\&
\&    print $declared\->description;
